<h2>Welcome to RESTx!</h2>
<p>The fastest and easiest way to create RESTful resources
in your enterprise or in the cloud.</p>
<ul>
 <li>As a user: Use the RESTful server API to encapsulate and share
     your knowledge by creating useful data resources, easy to handle
     and share with colleagues, customers or anyone else.</li>
 <li>As a developer: Transform your custom code into reusable entities
     by integrating them into the RESTx server, using the easy component
     API, which gives you a choice of several implementation languages.
</ul>
<p>Find out more about the RESTx project, view detailed documentation
and examples, tutorials, howtos and connect to the RESTx developer and
user community at the official project web-site: <a target="_blank" href="http://restx.mulesoft.org">http://restx.mulesoft.org</a></p>
<p><a target="_blank" href="http://restx.mulesoft.org">RESTx</a> is freely distributable under the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt">GPLv3 License</a>.</p>
